name: QueryParserTest
description: Unit tests for the QueryParser class, focusing on parsing and evaluating CSS selectors.

test_cases.name: testConsumeSubQuery
test_cases.description: Tests the ability to select elements using CSS selectors and verify their text content.

test_cases.name: testImmediateParentRun
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of a CSS selector into an S-expression representing immediate parent relationships.

test_cases.name: testOrGetsCorrectPrecedence
test_cases.description: Tests the correct precedence of OR operations in CSS selector parsing.

test_cases.name: testParsesMultiCorrectly
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of a complex multi-part CSS selector into an S-expression.

test_cases.name: exceptionOnUncloseAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests that an exception is thrown when parsing an unclosed attribute in a CSS selector.

test_cases.name: testParsesSingleQuoteInContains
test_cases.description: Tests that an exception is thrown when parsing a CSS selector with an unclosed single quote in a contains pseudo-class.

test_cases.name: exceptOnEmptySelector
test_cases.description: Tests that an exception is thrown when parsing an empty CSS selector.

test_cases.name: exceptOnNullSelector
test_cases.description: Tests that an exception is thrown when parsing a null CSS selector.

test_cases.name: okOnSpacesForeAndAft
test_cases.description: Tests that the parser correctly handles CSS selectors with leading and trailing spaces.

test_cases.name: structuralEvaluatorsToString
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing and string representation of structural evaluators in CSS selectors.

test_cases.name: parsesOrAfterAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests the parsing of OR operations following an attribute selector in CSS selectors.
